# How can I get Git to truly *ignore* line endings?
# https://stackoverflow.com/questions/22513269/how-can-i-get-git-to-truly-ignore-line-endings#answer-30631336
* -text

#sources
*.c -text
*.cc -text
*.cxx -text
*.cpp -text
*.c++ -text
*.hpp -text
*.h -text
*.h++ -text
*.hh -text

# Compiled Object files
*.slo binary
*.lo binary
*.o binary
*.obj binary

# Precompiled Headers
*.gch binary
*.pch binary

# Compiled Dynamic libraries
*.so binary
*.dylib binary
*.dll binary

# Compiled Static libraries
*.lai binary
*.la binary
*.a binary
*.lib binary

# Executables
*.exe binary
*.out binary
*.app binary
